title: Best of CCK: Jenga Drama
description:
The Jenga Draft caused a ton of controversy. Feits cuts a deal with Kayce for no reason in particular. Kayce has a strategy for winning Jenga and it relies hevily on he pants. Sandstorm is a mood. Unnecessary Roughness drama.
